  "text": "To validate the effectiveness of our proposed model, evaluations are conducted on three benchmarking review datasets from IMDB and Yelp data challenge (including Yelp13 and Yelp14) [CITATION_1] . Experimental results show that our algorithm can outperform baseline methods by large margins. Compared to the state-ofthe-art method, DUPMN made 0.6%, 1.2%, and 0.9% increase in accuracy with p-values 0.007, 0.004, and 0.001 in the three benchmark datasets respectively. Results show that leveraging user profile and product information separately can be more effective for sentiment predictions.",
